-- Credit Suisse, BofA Among Banks Paying $49.5 Million in Refco Fraud Case
-- David Glovin
-- 2010-04-21T22:05:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/credit-suisse-bofa-among-banks-paying-49-5-million-in-refco-fraud-case.html

          
          
             Units of Credit Suisse Group AG,
Bank of America Corp., Goldman Sachs Group Inc. and other banks
have agreed to pay $49.5 million to settle an investor suit
about fraud at Refco Inc., according to court papers.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
